{"tid":689584,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【6月4日】盟軍佔領軸心國首都","createTime":"2018-06-04T07:42:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-04T11:53:16.000Z","uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"553bee8a31b0edfe4aeebcee3e7744a51983671f","tid":689584,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T07:42:53.000Z","msg":"1944年6月4日，美軍第5軍團前鋒進入已被設為「不設防城市」的羅馬，該城也成為二戰首坐落入盟軍手中的軸心國首都。<br />\n<br />\n英美為首的盟軍早在1944年1月底就發起對羅馬的攻擊，當時英軍從義大利半島一路北上，美軍則從羅馬東南方的安其奧進行兩棲登陸，但受到地形限制與德軍堅守，英軍在卡西諾山的攻勢打了4個月才獲進展；美軍灘頭堡也直到5月底才發起成功攻擊，突破德軍防線，甚至差點截斷德軍第10軍團退路。<br />\n<br />\n6月2日，德國第10軍團殘部（大約7個師）成功撤退後，負責防衛羅馬的德軍第14軍團也放棄防線後撤、且戰且走，戰區司令凱塞琳元帥宣布羅馬為「不設防城市」，美軍則在6月4日清晨進占羅馬。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/6%E6%9C%884%E6%97%A5%E8%BB%8D%E5%8F%B2%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E4%BB%8A%E5%A4%A9-%E7%9B%9F%E8%BB%8D%E5%8D%A0%E9%A0%98%E7%BE%85%E9%A6%AC-160000353.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F6%25E6%259C%25884%25E6%2597%25A5%25E8%25BB%258D%25E5%258F%25B2%25E4%25B8%258A%25E7%259A%2584%25E4%25BB%258A%25E5%25A4%25A9-%25E7%259B%259F%25E8%25BB%258D%25E5%258D%25A0%25E9%25A0%2598%25E7%25BE%2585%25E9%25A6%25AC-160000353.html&d=gqSN%2BKN5GisA85iYsxYcAQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=f7989559\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/6%E6%9C%884%E6%97%A5%E8%BB%8D%E5%8F%B2%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E4%BB%8A%E5%A4%A9-%E7%9B%9F%E8%BB%8D%E5%8D%A0%E9%A0%98%E7%BE%85%E9%A6%AC-160000353.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4e46778a4efb81eecddab0005d07c5ca86af784","tid":689584,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T08:39:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"699e48cc951bb2c41b7d1d2d8909cbbd6f5337a0","tid":689584,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T10:14:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a393e